        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "<p><strong>Dive Into the World of Hours & Minutes with Accutime!</strong></p><p><strong>Transform Ordinary Spaces into Extraordinary Places!</strong></p><p>Let Sonic guide your little one through the world of hours and minutes. Step into a world of gaming excitement with this game themed Wall Clock from Accutime!</p><p>A 12-inch battery-operated wonder that's more than just a timekeeper! It's a lively burst of hues that bring joy to any kid's room or classroom. With its lively design inspired by the exciting world of Sonic, this clock doesn't just tell time; it paints it with a palette of laughter and endless possibilities!</p><p><strong>A Splash of Colors, A Dash of Learning!</strong></p><p>Watch as your children's eyes light up with excitement! This battery-operated wall clock is a playful masterpiece, adorned with lively hues that will brighten up any space. Its clock design makes learning the time an adventure, turning education into a captivating journey. Every glance at this clock becomes a delightful opportunity for your kids to enhance their time-telling skills in the most enjoyable way possible.</p><p>Note: This wall clock is operated by one AA battery (not included).</p><p><strong>Bring Home the Magic</strong></p><p>Why settle for the ordinary when you can have extraordinary? Our Sonic printed wall clock transports your little ones to the heart of their favorite gaming world. Plus, it's an ideal addition for both educational spaces and play areas.</p><p>Let the fun of learning to tell time begin! Click 'Add to Cart' now and watch as your kids learn to tell time with smiles and laughter, making every minute an adventure in the world of Sonic.</p>",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
